Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:07.68,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(370,370)\blur7.5\pos(315,1068)}{\1cBCE347}暴風雨{\1cFFFFFF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1005,1050)}你才是  利瑪的所在位置已經有頭緒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了這種事以為我會原諒你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前說好的完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  你這傢伙真能派上用處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我說出這種話  真是失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}那麼這之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再敢嘴硬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就幹掉你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  知道這些就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來這邊會處理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颱風仍舊保持原來的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預測將於後天橫渡靛藍花園
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  究竟會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看多蒙那麼慌張的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會是大事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長筒靴在哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那個的話  什麼都做不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…能還給多蒙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是對他很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  颱風究竟是什麼哞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大片雲滾滾而現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後裏面會有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那何止是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在我還是8歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同子彈一般的豪雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿刺人肺腑的雷電
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令房屋搖晃的呼嘯大風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那場暴風雨之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一位女性把傘借給了當時全身濕透往家裏趕的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的笑容相當迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}沒錯  相當迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  已經這個時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已經睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會在16歲時和她在附近的咖啡店再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫美智子  相當不錯的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我連她的眼睛都不敢直視
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的初戀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把燈關了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  現在回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那場颱風正是我們相遇的契機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人懷念啊  美智子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真是不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然方法很原始  不過這是最有效率的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是花園內的監控攝像機畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先試著調出了這三天的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  那個叫利瑪的特徵是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我可愛的小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  誰在乎那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是利瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾和佳音就把那裏的木材按照尺寸鋸好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅能幫我把那裏的盆栽搬到店裏去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盆栽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅也要來敲敲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅  不可以哞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能隨便使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼哞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用力量了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木材我送上來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來你們  沒被捲入什麼危險的事件裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在要去摘晚飯用的蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能來幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把大家的份一起摘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的份？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是唯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對不起  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙  我把你平時需要的麵包拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裏幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做防颱風準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待會幫你的店也查看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵包我幫你放進店裏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你們在修理屋頂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是凝聚了瓦洛夫家技術精髓的產品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其名為瓦洛夫R7
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是什麼哞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是極品的黑毛牛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫亞歷山德拉三世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是以優質的穀物作為飼料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以肉質非常嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有發現什麼好東西嗎  小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}我們已經掌握了利瑪所在的花園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}不過確定具體位置還需要一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力的樣子也好惹人憐愛啊  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}要是那麼迫不及待的話  你那邊也去給我收集點情報來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去還不夠華麗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們見識下我引以為豪的品位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  準備好了嗎羅曼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先按下右上的啟動開關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟動開關  ON
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右控制桿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右控制桿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有緊急突進的危險  絕對不要碰…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左控制桿是剎車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了大家總算在晚飯前完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來就是完工派對了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  快嘗一下我烤的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定非常好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這可是我烤出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃點蔬菜  肉的話待會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  難得剛烤出來  會涼掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  要吃什麼是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不允許有這樣的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你可是我的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說過別再這麼說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒有同意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅  是你吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  但是你嘴邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管什麼家庭情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為找到了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是石頭的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羨慕你呢  宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能專心做自己喜歡的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有其他想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  不用客氣盡情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個蔬菜是菲莉雅摘來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  摘的時候可厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜像在起舞一般
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在空中散成一片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起舞？  空中？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那種力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  再讓它們飛起來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事哞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一生氣肚子就餓了  有作為主食的咖喱吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場大風正適合作為新時代的開幕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是天命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將為吾等的吉夫特帶來繁榮富饒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後能成為引導者的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有擁有真正才能的  本咨詢會的各位賢人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門扉已經開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等的宿命正是迎接由星之大地所帶來的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與奇跡之子一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那是我的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫你那麼晚起來的哞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點的話就遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要去學校所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要派對  不要學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開吧  菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅  今天我們必須要去學校才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅還有不為人知淘氣的一面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾  學校  派對沒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢  昨天的派對很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  下次再辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去幫唯看一下她店裏的情況才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅  能拜託你看一下家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店裏今天休息  客人應該不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看家…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  看家  拜託你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是稍微想起點事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說今天停課
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  現在這樣沒法回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再避會雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  你剛才想起了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在和這很相似的地方  和我說了一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色石頭的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  誰都不相信媽媽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會找出證據  證明它是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是颱風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就直接點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  難道說在害怕我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太粗暴了  帕克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是重要的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不討厭聽到這種聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須快點回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  會淋濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等等哞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅  一定很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾  菲莉雅出事了哞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:13.83,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}胸に溢れる音が言葉に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:13.83,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}內心所涌現出的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:15.69,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}なりそうでならない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:15.69,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無法很好地表達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:17.85,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}見つめるだけだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:17.85,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}只是靜靜地看著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:22.47,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}それでもココロ繋がるような気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:22.47,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}即便如此仍感覺我們心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:25.80,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}いつも　近くにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:25.80,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無論何時  都想依偎在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:33.21,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}手を伸ばして触れるだけでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:33.21,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}即便只是伸手輕撫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:36.07,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:36.07,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}也會無比高興
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:44.20,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}どこからくるのこの気持ち　わからない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:44.20,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}這份感受究竟從何而來  不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:52.67,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}教えて　空はどうしてこんな広いの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:52.67,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}告訴我  天空為何這般廣闊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:56.32,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}広すぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:56.32,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如此地寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:59.69,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ほっぼり出したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:59.69,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}好想展翅翱翔其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:03.95,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}今にときめいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:03.95,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如今的這份悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:07.78,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}吸い込まれそうだから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:07.78,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}彷彿被深深吸引一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:19.56,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}強く　強く　掴まえて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:19.56,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}要緊緊  牢牢  將其抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相思念的那份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於將命運之門的鎖開啟了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  「彗星·路西法」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.84,0:23:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,重合的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一起將這冒險之票握入手中吧
